==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unplumb
<hw>Un*plumb"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>plumb</ets>.]</ety> <def>To deprive of lead, as of
a leaden coffin.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Burke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

